# ThreatForge Output — SIGNATURES
# CVE:       CVE-2026-60137
# Product:   wordpress
# Tags:      [KEV] [RCE] [T1] [POC]
# Score:     120
# Tier:      CRITICAL — ACT NOW
# Generated: 2026-07-21T06:00:38.461459Z
# Status:    OK
